  "description": "I learned today that I could migrate my old Grand Theft Auto Online account over, so I have. That\u0026rsquo;s pretty exciting, because it means that I have access to all the vehicles and properties that I used to have.\nBut, this also means that I should figure out the gameplay loop of these things - something I didn\u0026rsquo;t really do when I was acquiring them, and it\u0026rsquo;s changed a lot anyway.\n",
